<BlogLayout
  title="Is AI Music Ethical? Licensed vs Scraped Models, Explained"
  description="Whether AI music is 'ethical' comes down to two things: was the model trained with consent, and is there real human authorship in the track. Here's how licensed AI music actually works."
  keywords="is ai music ethical, licensed ai music, ai music consent, how is ai music trained, ethical ai music generator, is ai music stolen"
  slug="is-ai-music-ethical"
